EWN takes you through some of the things that US president-elect Donald Trump has said about South Africa. JOHANNESBURG US President-elect Donald Trump is quite the controversial leader, with extreme views on women, immigrants, homosexuals and South Africa.Eyewitness News takes a look at some of the things Trump has said about South Africa in the past.I really like Nelson Mandela but South Africa is a crime ridden mess that is just waiting to explode-not a good situation for the people!2. He has however, expressed his love for Madiba. 3. Last year (2015) Trump continued to bash South Africa saying it s a messAs I have long been saying, South Africa is a total - and very dangerous - mess. Just watch the evening news (when not talking weather).4. During the Oscar Pistorius trial in 2014, the controversial president-elect referred to Judge Thokozile Masipa as a total moron, likening the case to O.J Simpson s trail.The judge in the Oscar Pistorious case is a total moron. She said he didn&#39;t act like a killer. This is another O.J. disaster!